snippet.title: Gunhead - Release Date Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Strategize and attack with four guns locked and loaded in GUNHEAD, releasing November 8th.
Gunhead is an FPS roguelite that challenges players with boarding and neutralizing procedurally-generated alien starships to earn income for their Privateering enterprise. The decaying alien arks will defend themselves from intruders with a wide arsenal of cyborg monstrosities, robotics, and security systems, all obstacles that must be surpassed to achieve victory: the destruction of the ship’s central System Core.

#ps5 #ps5games #gunhead
